description: Bool identity must commute through nested Bool if expressions.
law: (= (fuzz-bool-id? (if {cond} (fuzz-bool-id? {p}) (fuzz-bool-id? {q}))) (if (fuzz-bool-id? {cond}) {p} {q}))
